node.text:
Limits for this evenings presale:

ALL OOO at (6) 4-pks per person
OOO mixed sixers (4) 6-pks per person
Character Glass (1) per person
Sticker Packs No Limit
Artist Prints No Limit

We will be conducting our normal presale tonight. Whatever we have leftover/extra will be released for walk-up sales.

The (6) brands posted this week are the only cans available on presale today, and then for pickup next week. Stickers, Character Glasses, and Artist Prints will be available for presale. ALL OTHER MERCH THIS MONTH WILL BE AVAILABLE FOR WALK-UP PURCHASE ONLY. THE PRODUCTS FOR PRE-SALE TONIGHT CAN NOT BE SHIPPED. IF ANYTHING IS LEFTOVER AFTER NEXT WEEKEND, WE WILL POST THE ITEMS ONLINE.

Out Of Order pre-sale begins promptly this evening (7pm EST, 4pm PST) over at rarbrewing.com (link in profile)

*MORE BELOW IN COMMENTS*

node.text: “Running Late” can #6 of #6 for our next OOO release Saturday 8/28 🥶 6.2% 🐱 Our lactose sour base conditioned on Carrot Cake, Cinnamon, Nutmeg, and our House Pastry Cream immersion blended with Cheesecake to emulate traditional frosting. This release will be heavily fruited and dosed at extreme levels. KEEP COLD 😉 Presale today, Friday 8/20 at 7pm through our web store.
